@startuml
title Proxy virtual - ahorro de recursos
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  interface Video <<Subject>> {
+play(): void
  }
  class HighResolutionVideo <<RealSubject>>
  class VirtualVideoProxy <<Proxy>>
}

Video <|.. HighResolutionVideo
Video <|.. VirtualVideoProxy
VirtualVideoProxy --> HighResolutionVideo : controla/delega
Main ..> Video : usa misma interfaz

note bottom of VirtualVideoProxy
Difiere la creacion del objeto real hasta que se necesita.
end note
@enduml
